Right now this folder is in a mess, will change later

Contains composer files, they will be removed to root directory 
Contains logic from forms and validates user input 


delete_todo.php -> Function for deleting todo from db.

login_verification.php -> Verification from login form.

register.php -> Redirects to page for registration because if email or username exits registion is displayed in register_validation.php  with error messages.

register_validation.php -> Sets user data into db and send mail to user email address to verify token, if that fails show registration form again.

send_email -> send_email function that uses PHPMailer and Gmail account

verify_email -> if user clicked on the link sent via email set his status in db to enabled and login to see homepage

todo_validation.php -> if the todo bar was not left empty insert user data into db 
